        {
            "articleHeading": "Moment: Welcome to Fidelity Stock Plan Services",
            "articleSubHeading": "Introduce your participants to Fidelity, help them navigate NetBenefits, and encourage key next steps including accepting grants, certifying their account and designating beneficiaries.",
