                {
                    "articleHeading": "Welcome to Fidelity Stock Plan Services messages",
                    "articleSubHeading": "Welcomes participants and helps them accept their award and/or open their account.",
                    "paragraphs": null,
                    "subArticles": [
                        {
                            "articleHeading": null,
                            "paragraphs": [
                                {
                                    "type": "STRING",
                                    "value": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><strong>Fidelity Sends:</strong><br /> Equity welcome message*: <a href=\"http://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_DOMEKIT_SAM.pdf\" id=\"Link_1632246197741\" title=\"US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1632246197741\" >US</a> | <a href=\"http://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_INTEKIT_SAM.pdf\" id=\"Link_1632246262542\" title=\"Outside US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1632246262542\" >Outside US</a><br /><br /><strong>You can distribute:</strong></div><div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">ESPP welcome message*:  <a href=\"http://www.myfidelitysite.com/sites/default/files/US%20ESPP%20EKit-%20ENH%20LEG.pdf\" id=\"Link_1632246316107\" title=\"US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1632246316107\" >US</a> | <a href=\"http://www.myfidelitysite.com/sites/default/files/OUS%20ESPP%20EKit-ENH%20LEG.pdf\" id=\"Link_1632246366894\" title=\"Outside US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1632246366894\" >Outside US</a></div><div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">Implementation welcome message*: US | Outside US (need urls)</div><div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">Implementation welcome flyer: <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/WelcomeFlyer_Equity_US.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633102931727\" title=\"US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633102931727\" >US</a> | <a href=\"http://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/WelcomeFlyer_Equity_OUS.pdf\" id=\"Link_1632246520491\" title=\"Outside US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1632246520491\" >Outside US</a></div>"
                                }
                            ],
                            "subArticles": null
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "articleHeading": "Onboarding Campaign",
                    "articleSubHeading": "Fidelity sends the following messages to help participants get started by setting up their account and learning more about their award.",
