                {
                    "articleHeading": "How To Guides",
                    "articleSubHeading": "How-to guides provide plan participants with detailed instructions for completing activities related to their award.",
                    "paragraphs": null,
                    "subArticles": [
                        {
                            "articleHeading": null,
                            "paragraphs": [
                                {
                                    "type": "STRING",
                                    "value": "<p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">Activate your account: <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_GEN_ACTINSTR.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633108356939\" title=\"US\" name=\"Link_1633108356939\" >US</a> | <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_INTL_ActivateInstructions.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633108376208\" title=\"Outside US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633108376208\" >Outside US</a><br /> Accept your grant: <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_Generic_OGADomestic.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633108403858\" title=\"US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633108403858\" >US</a> | <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_OGA_INTL_ACCEPT_GRANT.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633108425463\" title=\"Outside US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633108425463\" >Outside US</a></p><p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">Enroll in your ESPP: <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_DOM_ESPP_ENROLL.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633108457115\" title=\"US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633108457115\" >US</a> | <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_GEN_INTL_ENROLL_INSTRUX.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633108527792\" title=\"Outside US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633108527792\" >Outside US</a></p><p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">Exercise your award: <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_Exercise_DOM.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633108588476\" title=\"US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633108588476\" >US</a> | <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_OUS_EXERCISING_GRANT.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633108626590\" title=\"Outside US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633108626590\" >Outside US</a></p><p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">Sell shares: <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_TRADE_DOM.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633108816662\" title=\"US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633108816662\" >US</a> | <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_OUS_How_To_Trade.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633108855662\" title=\"Outside US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633108855662\" >Outside US</a></p><p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">Set up withdrawal preferences/transfer instructions: <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_US_EFT.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633108950902\" title=\"US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633108950902\" >US</a> | <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_GENERIC_WireTransferSteps.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633108992769\" title=\"Outside US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633108992769\" >Outside US</a></p><p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">Restricted Stock Awards (RSA) tax withholding: <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_Generic_RSTaxWithholding_Domestic.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633109079685\" title=\"US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633109079685\" >US</a></p><p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">Reinvest dividends: <a href=\"https://workplaceservices.fidelity.com/bin-public/070_NB_SPS_Pages/documents/dcl/shared/StockPlanServices/SPS_Generic_Dividend_Reinvestment_Domestic.pdf\" id=\"Link_1633109145775\" title=\"US\" target=\"_blank\" name=\"Link_1633109145775\" >US</a>  </p>"
                                }
                            ],
                            "subArticles": null
                        }
